        <item>
            <title>Adobe 公開一系列生成式 AI 實驗功能　預覽未來 AI 輔助編輯體驗</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/17/adobe-max-sneaks-2024/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=adobe-max-sneaks-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/17/adobe-max-sneaks-2024/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:30:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1269859</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Adobe 近年積極開發生成式 AI 功能，最近在他們的 Adobe MAX 活動上，就透過 Sneaks 環節公開一系列實驗性的生成式 AI 功能，讓觀眾一覷未來有機會實現的 AI 創作體驗。<br /><span id="more-1269859"></span></p><p>今年 Adobe MAX 活動上的 Sneaks 環節與去年類似，都把重點放在創作和編輯輔助工具上，為用家帶來更快快速、更精準的使用體驗，縮短不必要的處理時間。</p><p>Project Perfect Blend：方便將人物或物體加到另一張圖像中變得更容易，自動調整顏色、光線，甚至陰影以自然地融合。採用生成式 AI 幫助建立自訂背景，改善前景遮罩功能，特別是在自然的融合和逼真的陰影投射上帶來更佳效果，使整個過程更加順暢和逼真。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_89013"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xuPd0ZZa164?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Clean Machine:可以輕鬆地從照片或影片中移除不需要的閃光，比如相機閃光燈或煙花，以及短暫遮擋攝錄機的物體。甚至可以檢測並自動移除影片中的相機閃光，這在要清理畫面中不必要的元素時就非常方便。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_55246"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nq2b6GT18tU?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project In Motion：透過描述內容就可以將自訂形狀的動畫轉換成影片。也使用生成式 AI 根據初始的 After Effects 項目將文字轉換為動畫。此外，還可以加入風格參考圖像，將風格與提示混合搭配，創造獨特的效果。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_81332"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bT6ezwb0o6k?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Know How：透過數碼指紋識別和水印技術，快速追溯影片和圖像的起源，確認其創作者和 AI 生成記錄等，改善內容的透明度。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_47467"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hXwxlbusP6c?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Turntable：方便在 3D 中旋轉 2D 矢量數據，從任何新角度看都可以維持 2D 風格。即使在旋轉後，矢量圖形仍然保持原始形狀，方便維持原始設計。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_25966"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gfct0aH2COw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Super Sonic：使用提示為影片生成音效，或者點擊影片中的物體來生成音效。用家甚至可以透過聲音控制這些音效出現的時間，或者直接在時間線上加入和層疊音效、混合背景和前景音效，並從提示的選項中選擇以獲得合適的音效。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_36675"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RddSWodgX5w?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Scenic：透過提示建立 3D 場景佈局，使 2D 圖像建立變得更容易。這個工具可以控制相機並調整單一物體，引導圖像生成過程。透過更精確地編輯 3D 場景，可以減少調整佈局和相機檢視的試錯過程。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_11893"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RddSWodgX5w?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Remix A Lot：方便將草圖轉變為精美設計，用家可以從一個粗略的想法開始，然後使用一張靈感草圖來完善。工具使用生成式 AI 引導用家完成創作過程，可以調整設計以適應各種形狀和大小，甚至不規則的形狀，而且可以在不同的作品中維持風格統一。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_95834"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UGgdC3RvyMQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Project Hi-Fi：可以捕捉畫面的任何部分，並將其用作指南，快速建立高質素的 AI 圖像。然後，這些圖像可以輕鬆地導入 Adobe Photoshop 進行進一步編輯。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_30745"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iM8ejIpaqF8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>以上這些功能都是 Adobe 目前正在開發中的功能，最終可能會互相整合或者改變方向，但整體來説也是可以從中瞭解到未來 AI 普及化的情況下，各種創作的流程和方式都會出現變化，創作者們也需要與時並進了。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://blog.adobe.com/en/publish/2024/10/16/new-adobe-max-sneaks-transform-photo-video-audio-3d-creation">Adobe</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/adobe-introduces-adobe-content-authenticity-web-app/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Adobe 新工具保護創作者　方便標註作品版權並拒絕用作 AI 訓練</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/17/adobe-max-sneaks-2024/ai/">Adobe 公開一系列生成式 AI 實驗功能　預覽未來 AI 輔助編輯體驗</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
